			<td><a href="FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Callous Casting">Callous Casting</a></td><td>Spellcraft 1 rank</td><td>Include allies in the area of your spells to dishearten your enemies</td>
		</tr><tr>
			<td><a href="FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Friendly Fire">Friendly Fire</a></td><td><a style="text-decoration:underline" href="FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Precise Shot">Precise Shot</a></td><td>Increase your ability to attack in ranged combat by not caring if you hit your allies</td>
